      "short_description": "Secure Electronic Applications Limited is a private limited company based in Dartford, Kent, England, established in 1999. The company operates in the specialist construction and electronic systems sector, employing around 27 people and generating an annual turnover of £3,325,000.\n\nThe company specializes in providing warden call systems, access control, nurse call systems, and other electronic systems to housing associations, social landlords, and businesses in the southeast of England. Their services include design, installation, service, and maintenance of various systems, such as fire-detection and fire-alarm systems, burglar alarms, closed-circuit television cameras, and telemetry equipment. Secure Electronic Applications positions itself as an independent advisor, offering honest assessments and guidance on product advantages, maintenance costs, and lifecycle management.",
